Horizontal Scroll OffsetAddress: #BDE6 or #9FE6Default value: #00This register controls the horizontal scroll offset, if hardware scrolling is enabled.Legal values are:  *  0 to 79 in mode VGA80x40.  *  0 to 15 in modes 1a, 1, 2 and 3.  *  0 to 31 in modes 0, 2a, 3a, 4a, and 4.In modes 0 and VGA80x40, horizontal scrolling is in units of 1 character.In modes 1, 2, 3 and 4, horizontal scrolling is in units of 8 pixels.In modes 1a, 2a, 3a and 4, horizontal scrolling is in units of 4 pixels.